BEGIN_PGML

An archer draws his compound bow and shoots an arrow. The [`[$m]`] [`g`] arrow leaves the bow with a velocity of [`[$d]`] [`m/s`]. The power stroke of the bow is [`[$d]`] [`cm`]; that is, the bowstring exerts force on the arrow through a displacement of [`[$d]`] [`cm`]. The peak draw weight of the bow is [`[$f]`] [`N`]. (_This is the maximum force that the archer has to exert on the bowstring._)

*a)* How much kinetic energy does the arrow have after release?

[`KE=`] [_____]{"$ke"} [`J`]  

*b)* How much work does the bowstring do on the arrow?

[`W=`] [_____]{"$ke"} [`J`]  

*c)* What average force does the bowstring exert on the arrow?

[`F=`] [_____]{"$fave"} [`N`]  

END_PGML

